AgriGuru

Your AI-powered companion for smarter, sustainable, and successful farming.

About AgriGuru

AgriGuru is a next-generation digital platform designed to empower Indian farmers and agri-enthusiasts. By blending advanced AI, real-time data, and user-friendly design, AgriGuru delivers personalized crop advice, weather insights, government schemes, organic tips, and satellite-based crop healthâ€”all in your language.

What Sets Us Apart?

  • AI-driven, region-specific crop and farming recommendations
  • Integrated weather, satellite, and government data for holistic support
  • Multilingual support: English, Hindi, and Kannada
  • Modern, mobile-first, and accessible for all users

Our Inspiration

AgriGuru is inspired by the resilience, innovation, and spirit of Indian farmers. Our mission is to bridge the gap between cutting-edge technology and grassroots agriculture, making advanced knowledge accessible, actionable, and impactful for every farmer.
